snippet.title: Disney's ALIEN woke now? Amber Heard finds Motherhood. Spider-Man LEGO leaks!
snippet.description:
Noah Hawley described his alien TV show for Disney Plus as moving away from Ellen Ripley, and focusing more on class Warfare within Weyland-Yutani.

Amber Heard posted on Twitter that she is now a mother to a two-month-old daughter born through surrogacy. Sadly this is controversial even though it should be something that hopefully would be life-changing for her.

Spider-Man No Way Homes Lego sets leaked out today showing us a bit more about the upcoming web-slinger film.

SPACE JAM: A NEW LEGACY just keeps getting worse with the Porky P.I.G. Freestyle Rap

Indiana Jones is officially 122 years old!
